item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Amelia Lily - Be a Fighter
item.description:
The scrapped debut studio album by British singer Amelia Lily, originally planned for release on 29 April 2013.

Here it is in FLAC format. A deluxe version exists but remains unleaked, which included 4 new songs and 2 acoustic versions of album tracks.

Tracklist:
  1. You Bring Me Joy
  2. Party Over
  3. The Hills
  4. Shut Up (And Give Me Whatever You Got)
  5. Walk in My Shoes
  6. Just Can't Take the Rumours
  7. Promises
  8. Be a Fighter
  9. Over and Out
  10. Heartbeat
  11. Blue
  12. Truth or Dare
  13. Look Who's Laughing Now
